Fourth Department,

January, 1950.

(January 5, 1950.) Susan Spoor, Appellant, v. Nicholas Di Leo, Defendant, and Charlie Andrus, Respondent. Celia Taylor, Appellant, v. Nicholas Di Leo, Defendant, and Charlie Andrus, Respondent.

All concur. (The order appealed from changes the place of trial from Cayuga County to Wayne County.) Present — Taylor, P. J., Love, Yaughan, Kimball and Piper, JJ.
